<paragraph blockId="4.[448,816,1453,1477]" box="[448,816,1453,1477]" pageId="4" pageNumber="3232">
<heading box="[448,816,1453,1477]" centered="true" fontSize="10" level="2" pageId="4" pageNumber="3232" reason="3">
<taxonomicName authority="(Sowerby, 1833)" baseAuthorityName="Sowerby" baseAuthorityYear="1833" box="[448,816,1453,1477]" class="Bivalvia" family="Arcidae" genus="Barbatia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Arcida" pageId="4" pageNumber="3232" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="parva">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[448,618,1453,1477]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="3232">Barbatia parva</emphasis>
(Sowerby, 1833)
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[154,1111,1517,1732]" pageId="4" pageNumber="3232">
<emphasis box="[194,288,1517,1541]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="3232">Habitat.</emphasis>
Attached by a weak byssus to the undersides of rocks and coral rubble blocks.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection lastPageId="5" lastPageNumber="3233" pageId="4" pageNumber="3232" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="4.[154,1111,1517,1732]" pageId="4" pageNumber="3232">
<emphasis box="[194,335,1581,1605]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="3232">Distribution.</emphasis>
Has been found living only occasionally, but given its small size and camouflaged appearance it may have been overlooked.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[154,1111,1517,1732]" pageId="4" pageNumber="3232">
<emphasis box="[194,301,1645,1669]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="3232">Remarks.</emphasis>
May be taken for a juvenile of a larger, preceding 
<taxonomicName box="[924,1110,1644,1669]" class="Bivalvia" family="Arcidae" genus="Barbatia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Arcida" pageId="4" pageNumber="3232" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="undetermined">
<emphasis box="[924,1021,1645,1669]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="3232">Barbatia</emphasis>
species
</taxonomicName>
but it is of a pale brown colour, with soft periostracal hairs and umbos tinged pink to red.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[199,817,173,230]" box="[199,571,173,198]" pageId="5" pageNumber="3233">
<emphasis box="[199,278,174,198]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="3233">Range.</emphasis>
Indo-West Pacific [R/S].
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[199,817,173,230]" box="[199,817,205,230]" pageId="5" pageNumber="3233">
<emphasis box="[199,402,206,230]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="3233">Figured specimen.</emphasis>
<quantity box="[415,514,205,229]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.59" pageId="5" pageNumber="3233" unit="mm" value="15.9">15.9 mm</quantity>
, NMW.Z.1999.073.00006.
</paragraph>
